## Development Workflow

- **Feature branches**: `feature/GH-N-backend` — one branch per issue, suffix `-backend` to allow parallel frontend work
- **Commits**: Descriptive imperative English — `Add user creation endpoint`
- **Branch naming**: Never work directly on `main`
- **Scripts**:

```bash
npm run dev            # Start Nuxt dev server (frontend + server together)
npm test               # Run Vitest unit tests
npm run test:watch     # Watch mode
npm run typecheck      # vue-tsc type check
npm run lint           # ESLint
npm run lint:fix       # ESLint with auto-fix
npm run prisma:studio  # Open Prisma Studio (DB GUI)
```
